(firstQuint)The Effectiveness of L-ornithine-L-aspartate (LOLA) on Plasma Ammonia in Cirrhotic Patients After TIPS.

 Patients with successful TIPS deployment are randomized to LOLA arm and blank control arm.

 Plasma ammonia concentrations are measured before TIPS, day 1, day 4 and day 7 after TIPS.

